            "success": "The target sheds bright light in a 20-foot emanation (and dim light to the next 40 feet) and becomes fascinated with itself for 1 round. It must spend at least 1 action on its turn on a taunting display of arrogance or overconfidence. Using actions that include such a display\u2014such as using Perform to show off\u2014count toward this requirement.",
